        <Parent_String>Protestantism [300073735], Christianity [300073711], Abrahamic religions [300385986], religions (belief systems, cultures) [300073708], religions and religious concepts [300055980], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
